<plot>Belinda Carlisle's first solo video, produced to coincide with her first album. Contains not just songs, but also behind-the-scenes footage and interviews. Songs include I Need A Disguise, I Never Wanted A Rich Man, Gotta Get To You, Shot In The Dark, We Got The Beat, Band Of Gold, Lust To Love, From The Heart, Mad About You, Since You've Gone, Head Over Heels, and I Feel The Magic.</plot><url>http://localhost:8983/solr/movie.html?064465</url></doc>
